            <p> <b>S</b>elf <b>M</b>yofascial <b>R</b>elease is a method of self-massage which focuses on releasing tension in the neruomuscular system and net of tough connective tissue which surrounds the muscle fibers. </p>
            <p> Since it utilizes your own bodyweight to adjust pressure, it can be practiced just about anywhere with minimal equipment to provide slow, sustained pressure to specific trigger points. </p>
